title: STULZ Clima Unit: Temperatures
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/stulz
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This plugin polls the air temperature of all connected clima units on a stulz management.
 It is possible to define levels for warning and critical temperature. The plugin return
 {CRIT} or {WARN} if the current temperatue is higher then one of the levels.

item:
 The type of the sensor (e.g. {{unit air}}, etc.) and the index of the sensor seperated by a {{-}}

inventory:
 One service is created for each device.

